{"tid":1356121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不如大家試著不要說林鄭, 盧偉聰.","createTime":"2019-07-23T12:18:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T12:18:50.000Z","uid":155902,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d5128b80dc241130da19abb823254b5d6e54a5a8","tid":1356121,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:18:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">而係對準中聯辦, 鄧炳強, 同</span></strong></span><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">雙普選!!!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我明果兩件係抵屌, 但成日係度集中叫果兩個walking dead 落台仲乜, 盧偉聰11月點都走, 林奠應該都距離壽終正寢不遠.<br />\n明眼人都知而家中聯辦鄧炳強揸旗, 姓鄧果條仲要11月就上馬, 我地點都要係佢未上馬前拉佢落黎!!!<br />\n<br />\n仲有最緊要既雙普選呀, 要制度上有根本性既改革香港先至有希望呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}